{"tid":505449,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★老千！蘋果承認在 iOS 11.2 更新中 故意把舊款iphone變慢！","createTime":"2017-12-21T06:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T09:09:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a88b92e513e6429689dbc781bf04813c747f2a44","tid":505449,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:40:17.000Z","msg":"蘋果在回覆外國傳媒《TechCrunch》的查詢時指出，他們推出了最新更新，以防止 iPhone 6、6s 以及 SE 突然關機的情況，而方法就是把電池老化、電池溫度降低，又或者電池餘量變低時，減低處理器速度。<span style=\"color: red;\">蘋果更承認在 iOS 11.2 更新當中，把這個機制應用到 iPhone 7 身上，更加會「在未來為其他產品加入相同的支援」。</span><br />\n<br />\n在早前 Reddit 討論區有網友 TeckFire 提供更換電池前與更換電池後的 Geekbench 跑分結果，發現在電池更換後，其 iPhone 6 Plus 的跑分結果竟有大幅度提升，證明了蘋果的講法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/21/iphonebattery/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2Fiphonebattery%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=pDKrl1Vp8gUPhiduO97o%2F9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=5297f77d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/21/iphonebattery/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"9f763bc3c85bc57197f60cfeaf554d62feeb890c","tid":505449,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75cb5e8d08117105c238a9483240611b4a18061","tid":505449,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma